All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Agent
    Agent class represents a single Agent object that is moving on the Graph
    AgentController
    AgentController class represents a group of Agents, that are corresponding to a current solution.
    AgentMovementData
    AgentMovementData class keeps data about Agent movement, List agentMovement - keeps data for each millisecond of movement (agentMovement.size() == number of milliseconds)
    AgentState
    AgentState class is responsible for establishing a correlation between String and Integer values of state.
    AgentTimeRatio
    AgentTimeRatio class keeps time for each Agent state: MOVING, WAITING, INITIALIZING, ARRIVED
    AgentTimeRatioData
    AgentTimeRatioData class keeps TOTAL time for each Agent state: MOVING, WAITING, INITIALIZING, ARRIVED TreeMap <Integer, AgentTimeRatio> agentTimeRatioTreeMap - keeps AgentTimeRatio for each Agent
    AgentVisual
    AgentVisual class is a visual representation of Agent in viusalization process
    AlertBox
    AlertBox class is responsible for displaying alert messages to User
    AnimationController
    AnimationController class controls animation process
    CollisionData
    CollisionData keeps data about collision events between Agents
    CollisionRiskData
    CollisionRiskData keeps data about rate of collision risk between two Agents during movement
    ColorChangerGUI
    ColorChangerGUI class is responsible for setting up color settings which include colors for different Agent States as well as vertices
    ColorSetter
    ColorSetter keeps data about color settings
    Coordinate
    Coordinate class represents data about an Agent location on Cartesian coordinates system
    DataReader
    DataReader class reads data from input files
    DataSet
    DataSet class encapsulates data from input files and transports it to Business module.
    DistanceData
    DistanceData keeps data about distance between two Agents during movement
    DoubleAgentStatisticsGUI
    DoubleAgentStatisticsGUI class controls window that displays statistics data for two Agents
    Edge
    Edge class represents an edge on the Graph
    Graph
    Graph class represents a graph on which Agents are moving
    GraphController
    GraphController class represents a structure of Graph and its group of Agents.
    GraphVisual
    GraphVisual is Graph visual representation in visualization process
    GroupAgentStatisticsGUI
    GroupAgentStatisticsGUI class controls window that displays statistics data for group of Agents
    HelpGUI  
    LoadFileGUI
    LoadFileGUI class controls window that enables User to upload input files and create new solution
    MainController
    MainController class controls operations with GraphControllers as well as other business logic operations.
    MainGUI
    MainGUI class controls the whole GUI experience
    MovementAnalyzer
    MovementAnalyzer class generate AgentMovementData for each Agent, analyzes Agents movement, searching for collisions and calculating rate of collision risk between Agents
    PhotoOutputController
    PhotOutputController class is responsible for controlling photo taking process
    Plan
    Plan class represents a schedule of Agent movements on a Graph
    ShortestDistanceData
    ShortestDistanceData class calculates shortest path distances using BFS algorithm and compares it with an actual path distance, if an actual path distance is greater than shortest distance, then path is not optimal
    SingleAgentStatisticsGUI
    SingleAgentStatisticsGUI class controls window that displays statistics data for single Agent
    SolutionParametersGUI
    SolutionParametersGUI class controls window that displays data about solution: solution name, number of agents, amount of vertices as well as density of graph, etc..
    SpaceTimeData
    SpaceTimeData class keeps data about where in time and space is an Agent - its Coordinates and Time values.
    StartGUI
    Starts the whole application run-time
    StatisticsData
    StatisticsData class keeps all calculated statistical data
    Step
    Step class represents a structural unit of an Agent movements on a Graph
    TimeInterval
    TimeInterval class represents delta between start time moment of movement and finish time moment of movement
    VectorData
    VectorData class keeps vector coordinates and performs basic calculations on vector
    Vertex
    Vertex class represents a vertex on a Graph
    VideoOutputController
    VideoOutputController is responsible for controlling video recording process
    VideoSettingsGUI
    VideoSettingsGUI class is responsible for window that enables User to manipulate photo and video process
